            "description": "Synthesis of electroactive cell substrates for tissue engineering applications based on synthetic polymers. Combination of hydrophilic/hydrophobic properties to modulate the mechanical and wettability properties and introducing conductive particles. Physical-chemical characterization by calorimetric (DSC, TGA), mechanical (DMA, rheometer), and electrical (DRS) techniques. The morphological characterization will be made with electron microscopy and the composition with FTIR. The biologic evaluation carried out through in vitro cultures, cytotoxicity analysing, cell adhesion, proliferation and differentiation.",
